OL,3,CArmy barracks in Wales to host deep
OL,4,Cspace radar programme
OL,6,FAn army barracks in Wales is to be
OL,7,Fredeveloped to host a deep space radar
OL,8,Finitiative.
OL,10,FThe Ministry of Defence (MoD) has
OL,11,Fannounced that the Cawdor Barracks in
OL,12,FPembrokeshire will be the home of the
OL,13,FDeep Space Advanced Radar Capability
OL,14,F(Darc).
OL,16,FDarc will detect, track and identify
OL,17,Fobjects in deep space in collaboration
OL,18,Fwith radars from the UK's allies.
