OL,3,CArmy barracks in Wales to host deep
OL,4,Cspace radar programme
OL,6,FThe programme will see a network of
OL,7,Fground-based radars in Australia and
OL,8,Fthe US as well as the UK to provide
OL,9,Fglobal space monitoring, increasing
OL,10,Fthe AUKUS nations' ability to track
OL,11,Fobjects in deep space up to around
OL,12,F36,000km away from earth.
OL,14,FThe MoD say the capability will
OL,15,Fbenefit these nations' land, air and
OL,16,Fmaritime forces, as well as protecting
OL,17,Fcritical infrastructure and
OL,18,Fbenefitting domestic construction and
OL,19,Fspace industries.
