OL,6,FDefence Secretary John Healey said the
OL,7,Fproposed redevelopment "secures jobs
OL,8,Fat home and defence capabilities for
OL,9,Fthe future".
OL,11,FHe said: "Space plays a crucial role
OL,12,Fin our daily lives ` used by
OL,13,Feverything from our mobile phones to
OL,14,Fbanking services. It is also used by
OL,15,FUK defence to conduct vital tasks such
OL,16,Fas supporting military operations,
OL,17,Fnavigating forces and gathering
OL,18,Fintelligence.
