OL,3,CArmy barracks in Wales to host deep
OL,4,Cspace radar programme
OL,6,F"This new radar programme will not
OL,7,Fonly enhance our awareness of deep
OL,8,Fspace, but also help protect our space
OL,9,Fassets alongside our closest partners."
OL,11,FCawdor Barracks has been both a Royal
OL,12,FAir Force flying station and a Royal
OL,13,FNavy base.
OL,15,FThe site is currently home to 14
OL,16,FSignal Regiment, with the MoD in 2016
OL,17,Fsaying that the barracks would close
OL,18,Fno earlier than 2028.
