OL,3,CArmy barracks in Wales to host deep
OL,4,Cspace radar programme
OL,6,FThe redevelopment of the site for Darc
OL,7,Fwould keep the site open, with a
OL,8,Fpermanent presence of up to 100
OL,9,Fpersonnel to operate and maintain the
OL,10,Fradar capability.
OL,12,FSecretary of State for Wales Jo
OL,13,FStevens said it is "an important
OL,14,Fproject for Wales".
OL,16,FShe said: "By enhancing our awareness
OL,17,Fand understanding of what is happening
OL,18,Fin space, we can continue to ensure it
OL,19,Fremains safe, sustainable and
OL,20,Faccessible to all."
