OL,4,Cspace radar programme
OL,6,FThe Government has committed to
OL,7,Fengagement with the local community in
OL,8,Fdeveloping proposals for Darc, saying
OL,9,Fthere will be two local public
OL,10,Finformation events prior to the
OL,11,Fstatutory consultation period that is
OL,12,Frequired by Pembrokeshire County
OL,13,FCouncil.
OL,15,FMembers of the MoD Darc programme team
OL,16,Fwill attend these events to discuss
OL,17,Fthe proposals, answer any questions
OL,18,Fand hear local community views.
